{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban plastic for being used to attach tags/labels to clothes.",
        "additional_details": "Plastic shouldn't be used in clothes because well the small amount to attach the label is just cut away, then thrown away, it's such a waste and potentially harmful to the environment.",
        "background": "Make sure recyclable/reusable alternatives are used to attach clothes labels/tags and ban plastic as a means to attach.",
